item.description:
Slaves and prisoners of war from across the lands are brought to this brutal arena where they are tested in mortal combat.
The Hyborian Arena is a place to teach the basics of combat in the Conan 2d20 system. To prepare you should;
 Create a character Create a Roll20 account  Some of the features include;
 Arena map from classic Conan tile set Rule references from core rule book Doom and Momentum counters  Although designed as a tutorial for single sessions, there is also a campaign element to this game.
